WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:01.697
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:01.697 --> 00:00:05.220
I have another video I'm going to do for you here.

00:00:05.880 --> 00:00:11.496
A lot of people are wanting to know, "Hey, how do you hear God the way you do?

00:00:12.113 --> 00:00:14.920
" and they want to know how I've had the visitations.

00:00:14.920 --> 00:00:17.211
They want to understand more about me and everything.

00:00:17.211 --> 00:00:21.840
I'm going to tell you this right now: I am nothing special.

00:00:22.900 --> 00:00:27.327
Why the Lord has chosen to do what He's done in my life, I have no idea.

00:00:27.327 --> 00:00:33.342
I haven't done any kind of real supernatural prayer compared to anybody else.

00:00:33.874 --> 00:00:36.240
I've been obedient, I can tell you that.

00:00:36.240 --> 00:00:41.257
When He tells me to do something, I'm quick to obey, or I try to at least.

00:00:41.257 --> 00:00:51.750
Like for the last video, I told you about being hesitant of coming on here and telling you things on YouTube because I had a gaping wound and I didn't want to come and expose that to everybody.

00:00:52.290 --> 00:00:54.463
I've been a very private person.

00:00:54.463 --> 00:00:55.697
I'm very reclusive.

00:00:55.697 --> 00:01:03.614
I have a lot of friends, but I do not try to be real social, even with my family.

00:01:03.614 --> 00:01:09.420
Even my family thinks I'm kind of strange, as far as my mom, my dad, and my brothers and sisters.

00:01:12.579 --> 00:01:12.793
I've just been really different.

00:01:12.793 --> 00:01:16.170
That's the way I've been a lot in my life.

00:01:16.170 --> 00:01:17.820
I pray a lot.

00:01:20.710 --> 00:01:23.885
I have a very unique relationship with the Lord as far as the way I look at Him and the way I talk.

00:01:24.163 --> 00:01:25.335
I'll say that much.

00:01:25.335 --> 00:01:28.799
It all started when I was a little boy.

00:01:29.253 --> 00:01:33.805
I had bad learning disabilities all through school.

00:01:33.805 --> 00:01:40.167
I couldn't read, I couldn't write very well, I couldn't spell, and I couldn't do math.

00:01:40.167 --> 00:01:46.920
I went through school in special ed programs my whole entire life.

00:01:46.920 --> 00:01:48.787
People made fun of me a lot.

00:01:48.787 --> 00:01:54.533
I got bullied every day at school, spit on, pushed down, picked on all day long.

00:01:54.533 --> 00:01:58.460
I would come home and cry myself to sleep because of being bullied all the time.

00:01:58.460 --> 00:02:02.294
And so, I got up into my high school years.

00:02:02.294 --> 00:02:07.988
I still couldn't read very well, I still couldn't write very well, and I couldn't do math.

00:02:07.988 --> 00:02:19.799
So the principal came to my mom and said, "Some kids are just probably going to be like bricklayers.

00:02:20.999 --> 00:02:23.400
Your son really has a hard time.

00:02:23.400 --> 00:02:36.324
He's making zeros in school, he's not able to keep up, and so I would try to encourage you to just pull him out of school and let him get a trade.

00:02:36.324 --> 00:02:40.987
Let him go ahead and just work with his hands and go on with his life.

00:02:40.987 --> 00:02:44.250
He's not passing any classes; he's flunking out.

00:02:47.100 --> 00:02:54.447
I hate to say this, but I would just encourage you to go ahead and let him get a full-time job and go on with his life.

00:02:54.447 --> 00:02:58.760
" So I dropped out of school and started sacking groceries.

00:02:58.760 --> 00:03:01.739
I sacked groceries for three years.

00:03:01.739 --> 00:03:08.193
Prophecy after prophecy was spoken over my life that God had a call on me to do something big.

00:03:08.193 --> 00:03:09.700
I didn't know how to implement it.

00:03:09.700 --> 00:03:17.040
My mom and dad were going to Bible school at the time, and I was trying to get my GED.

00:03:17.040 --> 00:03:19.475
I thought, "Well, maybe I can get my GED.

00:03:19.475 --> 00:03:20.651
" I couldn't get my GED.

00:03:20.651 --> 00:03:23.660
I went and tried to take the test and I failed.

00:03:24.300 --> 00:03:29.431
So I gave up and just started working, and worked really hard.

00:03:29.431 --> 00:03:30.830
I started learning.

00:03:30.830 --> 00:03:33.494
I started listening to tapes from ministries.

00:03:33.494 --> 00:03:35.032
I got a tape player.

00:03:35.032 --> 00:03:43.155
I listened to ministries all day long, feeding on the Word of God, listening to Kenneth Hagin.

00:03:43.155 --> 00:03:45.506
And I know some people don't like Kenneth Hagin.

00:03:45.506 --> 00:03:47.168
I don't care what you think.

00:03:47.168 --> 00:03:51.204
Let me tell you that right there; I'm going to be bold with you.

00:03:51.204 --> 00:03:53.692
I do not care what you think about Kenneth Hagin.

00:03:53.692 --> 00:03:54.862
He changed my life.

00:03:54.862 --> 00:03:56.974
He taught me everything I know.

00:03:56.974 --> 00:04:00.420
So keep your comments to yourself in the comment section.

00:04:00.420 --> 00:04:05.159
If you do rude things and talk trash about him, I'll ban you immediately.

00:04:05.159 --> 00:04:07.200
There's no tolerance for it.

00:04:07.200 --> 00:04:13.350
So I listened to him over and over again.

00:04:17.052 --> 00:04:21.011
I found these ministries, I started listening to the Word, and I fed on the Word.

00:04:21.845 --> 00:04:26.186
The Lord started imparting to me.

00:04:26.186 --> 00:04:27.034
I started fasting.

00:04:27.034 --> 00:04:31.259
The Lord said, "I want you to start fasting every other day of your life.

00:04:31.259 --> 00:04:33.266
" So I did this as a teenager.

00:04:33.266 --> 00:04:35.567
I started fasting every other day of my life.

00:04:35.567 --> 00:04:37.140
I did this for years.

00:04:37.140 --> 00:04:38.940
I prayed, I fasted.

00:04:38.940 --> 00:04:46.418
I would start fasting when the sun came up, all the way to when the sun came down.

00:05:01.700 --> 00:05:02.040
Then I ate dinner, and that's what I did as a young man.

00:05:02.040 --> 00:05:07.260
I kid you not, I would spend time praying in the Spirit, reading my Bible, and listening to sermons.

00:05:07.260 --> 00:05:12.050
Then I got a job; I was offered a job.

00:05:13.226 --> 00:05:19.359
I had made some friends, and they said, "We want you to come and work in the ministry for us.

00:05:20.613 --> 00:05:25.193
" I thought, "Wow, here's my opportunity to preach," because I was 18 years old and I was excited.

00:05:25.755 --> 00:05:28.279
I got my first job; God opened the door for me.

00:05:43.220 --> 00:05:43.506
So I started cleaning bathrooms.

00:05:43.506 --> 00:05:46.460
The Lord said, "I want you to do that.

00:05:46.460 --> 00:05:49.560
" So I started cleaning for a mega minister's house.

00:05:49.887 --> 00:05:54.180
I started taking care of stuff for them, cleaning their cars, and doing this.

00:05:54.180 --> 00:05:56.480
I started learning and listening to him preach.

00:06:04.271 --> 00:06:04.643
I followed ministries, doing it over and over, just praying in the Spirit and learning.

00:06:06.682 --> 00:06:11.659
So the Lord spoke to us to move to where we are now, and I thought, "Man, this is my opportunity.

00:06:11.659 --> 00:06:13.852
" I was 20 or 21 years old.

00:06:13.852 --> 00:06:15.839
I had just got married.

00:06:15.839 --> 00:06:25.657
I had a prophecy over my life: "You're going to find your wife, and you're going to get married in a short amount of time.

00:06:28.045 --> 00:06:28.473
" So we got married.

00:06:36.983 --> 00:06:37.440
I thought, "Man, what's going to happen?

00:06:37.440 --> 00:06:38.677
We're going to move.

00:06:38.677 --> 00:06:44.580
" My mom and my dad moved to where they are, and they started a Boys Ranch.

00:06:44.580 --> 00:06:47.153
They started helping out with fatherless children.

00:06:47.153 --> 00:06:52.755
We started volunteering and helping out there, trying to help these troubled young teenagers.

00:06:57.915 --> 00:06:58.222
So we did that for about a year or two, and the Lord put us at a church.

00:06:58.222 --> 00:07:00.339
We started doing ministry at the church.

00:07:04.167 --> 00:07:05.550
I was cleaning there, and I thought, "Man, I'm going to have the opportunity to preach now.

00:07:05.550 --> 00:07:14.624
" Lo and behold, the pastor didn't like me that much because I preached too charismatic for him.

00:07:25.665 --> 00:07:25.987
So he said, "No, you can clean.

00:07:25.987 --> 00:07:27.884
You'll probably never preach here.

00:07:30.338 --> 00:07:30.556
" I thought, "Well, you're going to change your mind.

00:07:35.759 --> 00:07:36.119
I'm going to pray and fast, and God's going to change your mind.

00:07:50.331 --> 00:07:50.742
" So the Lord said, "Brandon, I want you just to be an armor bearer.

00:07:56.010 --> 00:07:56.550
You pray for the pastor here, and I want you just to keep being here and praying.

00:07:56.550 --> 00:07:58.155
" So I just kept cleaning.

00:08:01.365 --> 00:08:01.650
I cleaned 90 toilets three times a week.

00:08:01.650 --> 00:08:06.060
Every single time I was in there cleaning, griping in my heart, "God, You called me to the ministry.

00:08:06.060 --> 00:08:09.804
How am I going to do anything if I'm in here cleaning these toilets?

00:08:09.804 --> 00:08:12.575
What are You going to do with my life?

00:08:12.575 --> 00:08:15.766
Are You going to do anything with me?

00:08:23.520 --> 00:08:23.880
" So I just kept cleaning the bathrooms, cleaning all the floors, doing everything.

00:08:23.880 --> 00:08:30.132
And I'd go in there and ask, "Hey, will you let me preach or do anything?

00:08:30.132 --> 00:08:31.595
" "No, Brandon, you are a janitor.

00:08:37.071 --> 00:08:37.294
That's what you're going to do.

00:08:37.294 --> 00:08:38.724
You're not called to preach.

00:08:38.724 --> 00:08:40.513
We don't feel that about you.

00:08:40.513 --> 00:08:41.453
You clean.

00:08:41.453 --> 00:08:45.773
" I'd say, "But I know God's called me to preach.

00:08:45.773 --> 00:08:47.751
" They'd say, "No, that's not what we feel.

00:08:50.880 --> 00:08:51.540
" So I kept cleaning.

00:08:51.540 --> 00:08:54.945
The Lord gave me a word.

00:08:57.008 --> 00:09:01.520
I heard a word: "Hey, I want you to go warn the pastor that judgment is coming on him.

00:09:06.547 --> 00:09:06.760
You go tell him what I'm telling you.

00:09:18.473 --> 00:09:23.310
" I said, "They're going to fire me, Lord.

00:09:24.720 --> 00:09:25.320
I can't go in there and tell him that.

00:09:25.320 --> 00:09:28.587
He acts like he doesn't like me that much anyway.

00:09:28.587 --> 00:09:30.196
" "Are you going to be obedient to me?

00:09:30.196 --> 00:09:31.956
Are you going to be fearful of man?

00:09:34.013 --> 00:09:34.215
" I said, "Oh, man.

00:09:34.215 --> 00:09:34.620
Okay.

00:09:34.620 --> 00:09:43.847
" So I was standing in the back of the hall by his office on a Sunday night after church.

00:09:43.847 --> 00:09:48.780
Lightning was striking, and you could hear the storm blowing over.

00:09:48.780 --> 00:09:50.899
There was an actual storm happening.

00:10:02.820 --> 00:10:03.098
So I knocked on his door.

00:10:09.360 --> 00:10:09.660
He said, "Come in, what can I help you with?

00:10:12.885 --> 00:10:13.223
" I said, "The Lord has a word for you.

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:19.420
" So I gave him this word.

00:10:23.207 --> 00:10:27.729
I thought I had hit him, like just punching him.

00:10:27.729 --> 00:10:33.090
That's how strong the word was that the Lord had for me to give to him.

00:10:33.090 --> 00:10:36.637
I thought he was going to fire me right then.

00:10:36.637 --> 00:10:37.872
He didn't fire me.

00:10:38.610 --> 00:10:41.906
I think he was shocked because I came in there with such boldness, being just the cleaner.

00:10:41.906 --> 00:10:42.934
That's how it started.

00:10:51.380 --> 00:10:51.663
I started obeying Him on hard words.

00:10:51.663 --> 00:10:57.976
I started obeying Him whenever He told me to do something really hard, and then He started giving me more to do.

00:10:57.976 --> 00:11:00.300
He'd say, "Do this," while I'd be praying.

00:11:08.670 --> 00:11:08.992
He said, "I want you to go across town and give that pastor a word.

00:11:08.992 --> 00:11:19.104
There are three witches that are after his life, trying to kill him right now, and he's in the hospital fighting for his life.

00:11:19.456 --> 00:11:22.658
I want you to go and give him a word.

00:11:23.528 --> 00:11:23.963
" I said, "Are you serious?

00:11:23.963 --> 00:11:26.459
Lord, they don't know me!

00:11:26.459 --> 00:11:30.915
Are you going to do it or not?

00:11:30.915 --> 00:11:35.560
" So I said, "Yeah, sure, I'll do it.

00:11:35.560 --> 00:11:43.028
" So I took my little baby at the time, put the baby on my hip, and walked in through the doors.

00:11:51.344 --> 00:11:51.622
I said, "I have a word for your pastor.

00:11:53.185 --> 00:11:53.443
" The lady said, "I'm the secretary.

00:11:53.443 --> 00:11:54.870
What is the word?

00:12:07.956 --> 00:12:08.320
" I said, "Well, your pastor is sick and he's dying because of these witches casting spells on him, and I come to tell you Jesus is going to heal him and bring healing to this community.

00:12:08.320 --> 00:12:10.140
" She said, "You're right.

00:12:10.140 --> 00:12:13.109
Our pastor is really sick right now, and the doctors don't know what's wrong with him.

00:12:13.109 --> 00:12:14.879
" So I gave them the word.

00:12:14.879 --> 00:12:18.012
Well, that pastor started raising up; his church exploded.

00:12:18.012 --> 00:12:23.100
Then it fell because he committed adultery on his wife.

00:12:23.100 --> 00:12:24.385
Just things like that.

00:12:24.385 --> 00:12:27.977
So I have these words, and I give them when the Lord wants me to.

00:12:27.977 --> 00:12:29.993
I've just been obedient.

00:12:41.469 --> 00:12:41.820
It happens all the time.

00:12:55.465 --> 00:12:56.022
"I want you to pray for this person.

00:12:56.022 --> 00:12:58.187
Go and do this.

00:13:03.668 --> 00:13:03.930
" So I developed a relationship with Him.

00:13:11.494 --> 00:13:11.777
I kept working at it.

00:13:11.777 --> 00:13:13.873
Then He said, "Keep praying and cleaning these toilets.

00:13:13.873 --> 00:13:16.339
" Like I said, 90 toilets three times a week.

00:13:16.339 --> 00:13:19.313
This was a megachurch, a huge church where I worked.

00:13:19.313 --> 00:13:20.819
So I cleaned them.

00:13:20.819 --> 00:13:27.070
I'd go in there and clean them all by myself on a Saturday morning.

00:13:27.070 --> 00:13:38.246
I'd clean them all by myself on a Sunday night, clean them all by myself on Wednesdays a lot of times, cleaning the floors, waxing the floors, buffing the floors, keeping doing it.

00:13:38.246 --> 00:13:41.820
I said, "Lord, I'm doing what You've asked me to do.

00:13:41.820 --> 00:13:44.357
" But He said, "Well, you're not doing it in obedience.

00:13:44.357 --> 00:13:47.734
The willing and obedient will eat the good of the land.

00:13:47.734 --> 00:13:50.040
You've been obedient, but you're not willing to do it.

00:13:50.040 --> 00:13:52.440
You're complaining in your heart towards Me.

00:13:57.463 --> 00:13:57.681
" I said, "When are You going to release me from this?

00:13:57.681 --> 00:14:01.629
" He said, "When you can do it with full joy unto Me, I'll release you from this.

00:14:04.040 --> 00:14:04.253
Do it unto Me.

00:14:04.882 --> 00:14:05.890
" I said, "I can't do it, Lord.

00:14:06.092 --> 00:14:07.679
I keep doing this; this is terrible.

00:14:07.679 --> 00:14:09.900
I don't want to clean these toilets anymore.

00:14:09.900 --> 00:14:13.714
I do not want to wax these floors year after year after year.

00:14:13.714 --> 00:14:23.280
" Finally, as I told you about my little girl in the previous video, we had our little girl, and it took me even further down to the bottom of the ocean.

00:14:27.570 --> 00:14:35.906
With all that happening, all that's going on, I'm cleaning the bathrooms, I'm submitting to the pastor, and I'm praying for him even if I don't agree with what he's preaching.

00:14:38.914 --> 00:14:39.205
The Lord said, "Honor him.

00:14:39.205 --> 00:14:41.054
Do not touch him with your words.

00:14:41.054 --> 00:14:43.980
Pray for him, honor him, and respect him, even if you don't agree.

00:14:43.980 --> 00:14:47.580
But you have to not only do it with words; you have to do it with your heart.

00:14:47.580 --> 00:14:48.720
" "Are You kidding me?

00:14:57.566 --> 00:14:57.849
" I said, "Lord, this is the hardest thing I've ever been through in my life.

00:14:57.849 --> 00:14:59.674
You want me to do this?

00:14:59.674 --> 00:15:02.100
With my little girl, everything's falling apart.

00:15:02.100 --> 00:15:19.139
Now You want me to honor this man with my words and my heart, not complaining about cleaning these bathrooms, not complaining about my boss that's treating me like trash every single day, trying to get me fired, trying to conspire against me?

00:15:24.419 --> 00:15:24.939
" Because I could see in the spirit, I could warn of things that were going to happen.

00:15:32.066 --> 00:15:32.399
I would warn the pastor of the church about what was going on.

00:15:41.586 --> 00:15:41.784
So I started to develop a relationship with the pastor, and it took years of building.

00:15:41.784 --> 00:15:49.442
Then they came to me and said, "Hey, we know you can pray.

00:15:49.442 --> 00:15:55.187
People tell us all the time you're laying hands on people and they're getting healed.

00:15:55.187 --> 00:16:02.880
" So I started building a reputation of, "Hey, if Brandon prays for you, the Lord's going to heal you.

00:16:02.880 --> 00:16:06.883
" People on the staff started coming to me.

00:16:06.883 --> 00:16:10.295
"Hey, I've got a major migraine today.

00:16:10.295 --> 00:16:11.111
Would you pray for me?

00:16:24.630 --> 00:16:25.020
" The power of God would come and deliver them from a headache.

00:16:25.020 --> 00:16:27.660
"Hey, I'm fixing to sing on the stage.

00:16:27.660 --> 00:16:30.859
Would you pray for me?

00:16:31.079 --> 00:16:32.002
I have laryngitis.

00:16:32.002 --> 00:16:33.848
Will you pray for me?

00:16:33.848 --> 00:16:42.765
" Boom, the power of God hit them, and they would start singing, to be able to get through the service.

00:16:47.917 --> 00:16:48.185
It became a process.

00:16:56.699 --> 00:16:57.112
I'm the janitor that was cleaning and doing everything.

00:16:57.112 --> 00:17:03.577
Then people in witchcraft wanting to get free would come in there and get healed.

00:17:03.577 --> 00:17:07.559
None of them knew how to deliver anybody from a devil; they'd come and get me.

00:17:16.359 --> 00:17:17.773
I'm cleaning the toilets in church, or a vomit spill, or whatever from somebody getting sick, and they'd come and tell me, "Hey, we gotta have you in the back in the altar room.

00:17:18.127 --> 00:17:27.660
A witch just gave her heart to Jesus Christ, and she's flipping out, and we don't know what to do with her because she's growling and manifesting back there.

00:17:27.660 --> 00:17:34.140
Can you come back here and cast the devil out of her because none of us know how to do it?

00:17:36.340 --> 00:17:38.550
" I said, "Are you kidding me?

00:17:49.740 --> 00:17:50.120
You are pastors.

00:17:50.120 --> 00:17:58.020
" It was kind of an arrogance thing on my part because I was just like, "Whatever, you're coming to get me to do your job.

00:17:58.020 --> 00:18:00.330
" But I just said, "Okay, fine.

00:18:00.330 --> 00:18:04.590
" I had to be humble and just say, "Okay, I'll pray for her.

00:18:04.590 --> 00:18:09.315
" So I'd go down there and start casting devils out of her.

00:18:09.315 --> 00:18:14.580
They'd come back there and say, "Listen, you're taking too long, and it's too loud.

00:18:14.580 --> 00:18:22.791
Can you get her to be a little bit quieter because she's causing a distraction in church, and she's growling and everything.

00:18:22.791 --> 00:18:24.825
" I said, "Listen, you deal with it then.

00:18:28.809 --> 00:18:29.194
" Because I was already irritated about my circumstances.

00:18:29.194 --> 00:18:33.220
Lo and behold, this went clear on until about 11:30 at night.

00:18:37.371 --> 00:18:39.120
And so the pastors came in there and said, "Can you tell the devils to hurry up and get out?

00:18:39.120 --> 00:18:41.931
Because I'm ready to go home and eat.

00:18:53.892 --> 00:18:54.204
I don't want to be here anymore.

00:19:11.689 --> 00:19:12.000
" I said, "Go ahead and go home.

00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:14.460
I've got the alarm code and the key, don't worry about it.

00:19:14.460 --> 00:19:16.572
I'm going to get this girl set free.

00:19:17.340 --> 00:19:20.179
" So lo and behold, they all left.

00:19:34.947 --> 00:19:35.133
You know, that's the way things went.

00:19:35.133 --> 00:19:36.463
I started getting a reputation.

00:19:36.463 --> 00:19:39.180
That's the way I live my faith.

00:19:39.180 --> 00:19:48.570
I believe God is a deliverer, I believe God is a healer, and regardless of my circumstances and what's going on around me, He is a good God.

00:19:48.570 --> 00:19:50.387
And so they let me start doing prayer.

00:19:59.355 --> 00:19:59.737
So, I started doing Saturday morning prayer whenever the main prayer lady was gone.

00:19:59.737 --> 00:20:09.799
When I led prayer, the presence of God would fill that whole atmosphere, and people wouldn't move because the power of God would settle in so strongly.

00:20:09.799 --> 00:20:19.416
Whenever we would do prayer, it was nothing about me; it had everything to do with Jesus.

00:20:19.416 --> 00:20:26.220
I want to let you know, if God will use me, He will use you.

00:20:26.220 --> 00:20:30.149
I'm telling you, I'm nothing special.

00:20:30.149 --> 00:20:36.096
I'm just telling you about just being obedient to whatever the Lord told me to do.

00:20:36.096 --> 00:20:37.860
So, I just kept cleaning toilets.

00:20:37.860 --> 00:20:39.599
Ten years went by.

00:20:39.599 --> 00:20:42.559
On 3/3 of '13, the Lord says, 'You're done.

00:20:42.559 --> 00:20:49.080
' On 3/3 of '03, I was hired; on 3/3 of '13, He said, 'You're done.

00:20:49.080 --> 00:20:53.520
I want you to quit now.

00:20:53.520 --> 00:20:56.100
' I said, 'Are you serious?

00:20:56.100 --> 00:20:58.590
I don't mind being here anymore.

00:20:58.590 --> 00:21:01.455
' He said, 'Yeah, I know.

00:21:01.455 --> 00:21:02.730
That's why you're released.

00:21:02.730 --> 00:21:04.260
' A year goes by; He releases me.

00:21:16.877 --> 00:21:17.168
I stopped praying to be a part of doing that.

00:21:26.933 --> 00:21:27.105
He said, 'I'm going to do something different with your life now.

00:21:27.105 --> 00:21:28.283
' So, I stopped doing it.

00:21:28.283 --> 00:21:34.095
Six months goes by, and the pastor falls into an adulterous affair, and the church falls.

00:21:44.087 --> 00:21:44.495
It was a very hard thing for me because I thought, 'Man, this is terrible.

00:21:44.495 --> 00:21:48.217
' I warned him about all the things that were coming prophetically.

00:21:50.699 --> 00:21:52.740
I warned him about all of it, and he still didn't listen.

00:21:56.887 --> 00:22:02.430
I spent years telling him, and you know what?

00:22:02.430 --> 00:22:03.780
I did my job.

00:22:03.780 --> 00:22:05.805
I did my job.

00:22:05.805 --> 00:22:08.220
I did it, and I honored him.

00:22:20.850 --> 00:22:24.645
I prayed for him, and I did everything I could do.

00:22:24.645 --> 00:22:27.520
So, the Lord said, 'I want you to do something different.

00:22:27.520 --> 00:22:30.510
' So I thought, 'Man, I'm going to get into ministry now.

00:22:30.510 --> 00:22:30.996
' Nope.

00:22:43.800 --> 00:22:44.055
My daughter is still overcoming, and things are falling apart.

00:22:47.760 --> 00:22:48.060
The Lord said, 'I want you to start doing business stuff.

00:22:48.060 --> 00:22:48.960
I'm done.

00:22:48.960 --> 00:22:52.227
I don't want you to be in ministry anymore.

00:22:52.227 --> 00:22:55.860
I want you to do something different with your life, Brandon.

00:22:55.860 --> 00:22:58.363
' I said, 'Are you kidding me?

00:22:58.363 --> 00:23:01.589
I've had all these words, Lord, You've given me about ministry.

00:23:01.589 --> 00:23:05.391
' He said, 'I'm going to take you in a different direction now.

00:23:05.391 --> 00:23:06.033
It's okay.

00:23:06.033 --> 00:23:06.867
Are you serving Me?

00:23:06.867 --> 00:23:08.048
' I said, 'Yes.

00:23:08.048 --> 00:23:10.980
' So, I put it all on the shelf.

00:23:21.799 --> 00:23:22.019
I put ministry on the shelf.

00:23:22.019 --> 00:23:23.904
I started working and trying to make money.

00:23:23.904 --> 00:23:25.185
He would give me ideas.

00:23:25.185 --> 00:23:36.000
I would develop a relationship with Him, and I told you all about this: we'd sit on the couch together, and I'd practice the prophetic voice inside of me.

00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:39.827
He'd tell me about scores of football games.

00:23:39.827 --> 00:23:48.480
Because it's just the way this little guy goes, 'Well, Jesus is sitting on my couch, I won't ask Him about scores and about the games.

00:23:55.169 --> 00:23:55.424
I'm going to talk to Jesus.

00:23:55.424 --> 00:23:56.445
' Whatever, dude.

00:23:56.445 --> 00:24:01.407
You don't have a clue; you have no relationship with Him at all.

00:24:01.407 --> 00:24:03.059
I'm going to be real with you.

00:24:16.346 --> 00:24:19.655
If you get real, God will get real with you.

00:24:19.655 --> 00:24:24.980
These people that have all this religious Pharisee stuff going on inside of them, they're never going to be used by Him.

00:24:26.933 --> 00:24:31.880
I'm telling you, you've got to get real with God, and God has got to take you through the fire.

00:24:31.880 --> 00:24:37.466
He has to take you through trials and tribulations to develop your character.

00:24:37.466 --> 00:24:48.693
He'll take you through things, and He'll let you feel like you're going to drown, but it keeps building up inside of you, and He's trying to grow inside of you so that you have character.

00:24:48.693 --> 00:24:55.840
Because you have to die to self, and a lot of people don't want to die to self.

00:24:57.013 --> 00:25:00.539
You don't have the character to handle the pressure of the anointing and the things going on in your life.

00:25:00.539 --> 00:25:04.290
So you go through some things, and it's called the Refiner's Fire.

00:25:08.567 --> 00:25:09.453
And I'm telling you, my Refiner's Fire was cleaning poop, cleaning vomit, cleaning the babies' rooms, and doing all this stuff.

00:25:09.453 --> 00:25:14.169
Altogether, between the megachurch and the mega-ministry, I did it for thirteen and a half years.

00:25:14.169 --> 00:25:20.730
Cleaning and cleaning and cleaning, to the point where my hands had calluses and sores all over them from chemicals and doing things.

00:25:27.360 --> 00:25:27.630
So then He told me, 'Hey, I don't want you to do any ministry anymore.

00:25:27.630 --> 00:25:30.796
I'm going to take you and do something different in your life.

00:25:30.796 --> 00:25:32.240
' I thought, 'Are you kidding me?

00:25:32.240 --> 00:25:43.233
' So, in the process of all this, the pastor told my wife—because my wife was very smart; she graduated top of her class in high school—so she was doing accounting and working at the church too.

00:25:43.928 --> 00:25:50.142
And he told her, he said, 'If you go and get your degree, I'll put you head over the accounting department.

00:25:50.142 --> 00:25:51.933
' So, my wife started going to ORU.

00:25:51.933 --> 00:25:58.679
Doing this, my daughter's overcoming autism, we're pushing as hard as we can because we're tired of being broke, and we want more.

00:25:58.679 --> 00:26:02.359
We want more finances to be able to have a nice home.

00:26:02.359 --> 00:26:08.159
We're living in a shotgun rental house, barely getting by.

00:26:08.159 --> 00:26:09.697
It's terrible, I'm just telling you.

00:26:09.697 --> 00:26:12.882
We couldn't make our car payment; we're living on food stamps.

00:26:12.882 --> 00:26:14.855
We were doing everything we could.

00:26:14.855 --> 00:26:16.919
So, she's doing night school.

00:26:16.919 --> 00:26:21.500
We're pushing as hard as we can, doing it online, doing all we could.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
She gets her bachelor's degree in business and counseling.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.400
She's still not done, so I help her, and we get all the way through her master's, and she gets her master's in accounting.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Everything's fine.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
She makes a 4.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
0 through college; her whole college, she has a 4.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
0.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
She finishes her master's degree.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
She does it all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
It was a lot of work.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
My daughter's still overcoming autism, we have our son, we get through all of it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
We're finishing her college.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.350
I'm cleaning, barely making it the whole time, and he falls morally, and she's not able to get the job anymore.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
So, she has a master's in accounting and a 4.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
0.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.700
We have the degrees, we have all this stuff, and the Lord says, 'I'm going to do something different with your life.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
' So, we started to do some business stuff, and the Lord started blessing it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
He started doing this with us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
He started telling me where to go every day to find the stuff to do for our business.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
I started listening to Him in everything.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Seven years go by.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.450
Seven years I've put the call completely on the shelf, and He starts telling me, 'Brandon, are you going to be obedient to what I've called you?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
I want you to do a YouTube channel.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
' I said, 'What?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Are you serious?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
' I said, 'Lord, I'm doing good.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
I'm enjoying doing this.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
I'm listening to You every day on what to do with my finances.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
This is what You want me to do with my life?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
' I said, 'Surely I'm missing it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
' I said, 'This is kind of weird, it's like back and forth.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.750
' So He says to me, 'All that time, I wanted to see if you were serving Me or if you were serving the call.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
Now I have found that you're serving Me, and it's not just about the call.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
You've been obedient to what I've called you to do every step of the way.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.750
Now get ready, because I'm going to put you in ministry, and I'm going to open a door for you, and it's going to explode.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Be obedient to what I've asked you to do, and the doors are going to fling wide open for you for ministry now, because I have found that you fear Me, and you fear what I've asked you to do.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
You've been obedient.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
' And I said, 'Lord, I don't want to do it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
' Because, I said, 'My little girl is still overcoming.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
You want me to do a ministry?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
You want me to do all this stuff?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
' I said, 'I've run from it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
' I actually was relieved that He had told me to do business.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
Because He had told me to invest in things, and it was being successful.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
The Lord started blessing my hands big time, and I was excited about it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
And I said, 'Man, for the first time we're actually able to pay our bills on time.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
For the first time we're able to not have to be on food stamps.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.150
' It was embarrassing not being able to pay your bills, to not be able to pay your electric or your water or your gas because you're so broke.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.600
And every single time you get to the end of the paycheck, you'd have to borrow on a credit card to get through because we were trying to pay for my daughter to go through therapy.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
We had nothing.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
We were broke, dead broke, working for the church.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.250
And like I said, we got out of the church, and my wife got out of college, and we thought, 'Man, we're going to be in the money now because she's got her master's degree.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
' Nope.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
Nothing happened with the master's degree.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
She still doesn't use her master's degree as of this moment.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.700
She is able to do taxes, she is able to do everything she needs to do; she has a lot of education.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
So, this is the process we've been in our life.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
I say all this to say, I hope that was not boring.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
I'm just trying to tell you where I come from.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
It has been a lot of trials.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:17.500
There has been a lot of 'I don't know if we're going to make it,' standing every single paycheck, standing and believing, cleaning the bathrooms, dying to self, the trials, and developing my relationship with Him to the point of thinking, 'Man, Lord, if You're ever going to use me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
' And then He tells me, 'I'm not going to do that with you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
I want you to do something else.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
' And for years I think the promise is gone.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
God doesn't want me to be a preacher.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
He doesn't want me to do anything like that.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
I'm going to be a businessman.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
And so, all that to say this: I'm here, and that's where I'm at right now.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
That is a lot of testimony of everything that I've been through up until today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.450
