00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
So, let me pray for you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.950
If you have a dream, if you have some kind of call on your life, you feel God wants you to be in ministry, and you don't know how to get there, don't give up on it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
You know what?

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I don't know where this is going to lead.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
I don't have any clue.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
All I know is God told me to be on YouTube, and you all are watching it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.600
It's been very interesting for me because I now have 50,000 subscribers, and I started out, I believe it was February or whatever, doing these videos and putting ministry stuff on there, and people started subscribing.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
And He said, 'I'm going to breathe on it for you,' and that's exactly what He's done.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
So, I appreciate you all being a part of this.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Like I said, I have no clue where it's going to go.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.050
All I know is I wake up every day still doing my business stuff, working, and doing this whenever I have time to.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
I just want to say thank you for helping and supporting me and being a part of it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Like I said, I believe God has put healing in my hands.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
I feel the fire in my hands when I pray for people.

